(@@) مملكة الطبيعة(@)(@)(@@) Naturreich(@)(@)(@@) règne de la nature(@)(@)(@@) مملكة الغابات(@)(@)(@@) Reich der Zweecke(@)(@)(@@) règne des fins(@)(@)(@@) منفعة(@)(@)(@@) Interesse(@)(@)(@@) intérêt(@)(@)(@@) موضوع(@)(@)(@@) Gegenstand-Objekt(@)(@)(@@) Objet(@)(@)(@@) ميل(@)(@)(@@) Neigung(@)(@)(@@) inclination(@)(@)(@@) نية(@)(@)(@@) Gesinnung(@)(@)(@@) intention(@)(@)(@@) واجب(@)(@)Pflicht(@)(@)(@@) dévoir(@)(@)(@@) وجود(@)(@)(@@) Dasein(@)(@)(@@) existence(@)(@)(@@) وحدة(@)(@)(@@) Einheit(@)(@)(@@) Unité(@)(@)(@@) وسيلة(@)(@)(@@) Mittel(@)(@)(@@) moyen 
ms98	